Login by Facebook
-------------------------------------------
Need facebook id, secret key

If developer account not exist:
- go to developers.facebook.com
- get started (click)
- Register (click)
- continue
- contact info
	- primary email: your email
	- I agree (check mark)
	- confirm Email (click)
- About you
	- Developer (click)
	- complete registration (click)

If developer account exist:
- go to developers.facebook.com
- My Apps (click)
	- create App (click)
	Add use case
	-------------------
	Other (click)
	- Next (click)
	
	Type: 
		Customer 
	Next

	Details:
	- Add an app name: wewe.com.bd
	- App contact email: info@wewe.com.bd
	- Create app (button click)

	Add product to your app
	------------------------------------
	- Facebook Login
		- Set up (butto click)
		- web (click)
			- Site url: http://wewe.com.bd
			- Save (click)
			- continue (click)
			- Next

	click on "App Settings" (from Left side bar)
		- Basic (click)
		- App domains: https://wewe.com.bd/
		- Privacy policy URL: https://wewe.com.bd/privacy_policy/
		- Terms of Service URL: https://wewe.com.bd/terms_service/
		- User detetion instruction URL: https://wewe.com.bd/privacy_policy/
		- Category: select your website business type
		- Save change (button click)

	Now, click on "App Mode" (At the top)
			|____ Developer to Live (set)


	!!copy App_Id and Secret Key and use it in your project!!


